---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="AgentKitProject Terms of Service."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="template-notice">
        <strong>Template — not legal advice.</strong> This is a placeholder template. Review with qualified legal counsel before publishing.
      </div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="lead">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-body">
        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using AgentKitProject services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>

        <h2>2. Services</h2>
        <p>AgentKitProject provides tools for creating, sharing, and running portable Agent Kits, including AgentKitForge, AgentKitMarket, and related services.</p>

        <h2>3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and all activities under your account.</p>

        <h2>4. Agent Kit Content</h2>
        <p>You retain ownership of Agent Kits you create. By publishing to AgentKitMarket, you grant AgentKitProject a license to host and distribute your content. See the <a href="/legal/kit-license">Kit License</a> for default licensing terms.</p>

        <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to use our services for any unlawful purpose or in any way that could harm our services or other users.</p>

        <h2>6. Termination</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access to our services for violation of these terms.</p>

        <h2>7. Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>Services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For terms questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@agentkit-project.com">hello@agentkit-project.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .template-notice {
    background: #fef9c3;
    border: 1px solid #fde047;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    color: #713f12;
  }
  .legal-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
